I"Î<h1 id="cloud--lan">Cloud &amp; LAN</h1>

<p>ScummVM has two additional tabs: Cloud and LAN. This allows you to sync games and download game files from storage.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Cloud
    <ul>
      <li>Connecting Cloud Storage</li>
      <li>Game Sync</li>
      <li>Downloading game files</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>LAN
    <ul>
      <li>Running a web server</li>
      <li>Using webserver to upload/download files</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

